&gt;I ended up reworking my TestCase and changed my suite() to be:
&gt;
&gt;   public static Test suite() {
&gt;        TestSuite suite = new TestSuite();
&gt;
&gt;        String pathName = System.getProperty(&quot;test.path&quot;);
&gt;        String hostName = System.getProperty(&quot;test.host&quot;);
&gt;        String hostPort = System.getProperty(&quot;test.port&quot;);
&gt;
&gt;        System.out.println(&quot;Running test messages from: &quot; + pathName
);
&gt;        File path = new File( pathName );
&gt;        File[] files = path.listFiles();
&gt;
&gt;        for (int i = 0; i &lt; files.length; i++) {
&gt;            File file = files[i];
&gt;            if ( file.getName().startsWith(&quot;test&quot;) && 
&gt;file.getName().endsWith(&quot;xml&quot;)) {
&gt;                suite.addTest( new XmlMessageTest( &quot;http&quot;, hostName, 
&gt;hostPort, file ));
&gt;                suite.addTest( new XmlMessageTest( &quot;https&quot;, hostName, 
&gt;hostPort, file ));
&gt;                suite.addTest( new SoapMessageTest( &quot;http&quot;, hostName, 
&gt;hostPort, file ));
&gt;                suite.addTest( new XmlMessageTest( &quot;https&quot;, hostName, 
&gt;hostPort, file ));
&gt;            }
&gt;        }
&gt;
&gt;        return suite;
&gt;    }
&gt;
&gt;
&gt;Seems to be working fine.
